{"tid":2100234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧打「西藏牌」全方位抗華  美軍機廣東偵察 距大陸僅95公里","createTime":"2020-07-09T01:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T03:48:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2236265516cc58c463c6010bd7b0a98c90fb8c75","tid":2100234,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:57:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200709/NSLTRVJZFSHNVXTAZ7O3HXFSWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200709%2FNSLTRVJZFSHNVXTAZ7O3HXFSWU%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=ca4e7d5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200709%2FNSLTRVJZFSHNVXTAZ7O3HXFSWU%2F&h=049304f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200709/NSLTRVJZFSHNVXTAZ7O3HXFSWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧打「西藏牌」全方位抗華 <br />\n美軍機廣東偵察 距大陸僅95公里<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mKwUH16T6w42rEZQKMuJoGBXEfU=/713x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7JQVTNQJ35H2NWTWQQJM6HY3ZY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmKwUH16T6w42rEZQKMuJoGBXEfU%3D%2F713x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7JQVTNQJ35H2NWTWQQJM6HY3ZY.gif&h=e27a48a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美軍一架EP-3E偵察機昨日抵近廣東沿海偵察，距海岸僅95公里，為近來最近的一次。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國全方位展開對華行動，<br />\n。。。。。。起訴中共在新疆涉犯下的「種族滅絕和反人類罪行」。<br />\n<br />\n據追蹤美國軍機在台海周邊空域動態的推特顯示，美軍昨日上午又派出一架EP-3E電子偵察機，經巴士海峽靠近台海中線，再折向西南飛行，對廣東沿海抵近偵察，距大陸僅95.7公里，是美機連續第三日抵近大陸偵察，且距離大陸最近一次；前兩天距離為110至120公里。顯示美方對北京施壓力度加強。粵東、粵北及粵西分佈有中共導彈基地、空軍基地，而相鄰的福建、江西更有大量中共對台作戰陸、空和火箭軍基地；美機抵近偵察，目標不言而喻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對西藏官員實施簽證限制<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：FBI局長轟華干預大選<br />\n<br />\n至昨日為止，美軍已連續三日出動偵察機抵近中國大陸偵察，機型包括RC-135U戰略電子偵察機、EP-3E電子偵察機及P-8A反潛巡邏機等，每次均經台灣防空識別區。台國防部對此不作評論，僅強調對台海周邊海空域狀況，「國軍均充份掌握，並適切應處。」中國國防部發言人吳謙前日曾回應指，美國派軍艦軍機到東海、南海挑釁，對中方實施高頻度抵近偵察，嚴重危害中國主權與安全利益，解放軍「保持高度戒備」。國際危機組織（CrisisWatch）最新報告，把台海納入安全情勢「重大惡化地區」，與朝鮮半島、也門等相同。該組織表示，隨着中共不斷入侵台灣防空識別區，加上美中在該區對峙，令台海緊張局勢加劇。<br />\n<br />\n除軍事挑釁，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n惡劣的美方人員「實行簽證限制」報復。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n流亡疆人首藉國際法院問責<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n他們已向位於荷蘭的國際刑事法院提出80頁的投訴，要求調查中共在新疆涉「種族滅絕和反人類罪行」進行調查。<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n對中共在新疆犯下的罪行「可以有裁判權」。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/美國之音"},{"pid":"b520ed1cceea130fbc7bcf1220b6bcaf24d5a1ab","tid":2100234,"uid":278298,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:02:34.000Z","msg":"「國務卿蓬佩奧前日宣佈，將依 《西藏旅行對等法》（Reciprocal Access to Tibet Act），對涉阻礙美國人進出西藏的中共官員實施簽證限制。」<br />\n<br />\n仍然係軟弱無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a00e16bda8ae9196c8f7b5924c4a3cabb2db38","tid":2100234,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:11:33.000Z","msg":"好廢，只係限制唔係禁止，況且人哋唔嚟美國唔見有咩損失<br />\n至於什麼戰機喺上空飛過支軍成日做㗎啦，呢啲只係靠嚇嘢又唔會少條毛"},{"pid":"236afd0c3e591be81d98aae414cd83067a645cb4","tid":2100234,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"西藏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff7f0461c313bd3d323ea0b4edccde53454b5ab","tid":2100234,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95114d7956d67e4344379bf071648385cdeff0c","tid":2100234,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"制裁左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e972780823c905e1e10c24b52613203a97dfbc","tid":2100234,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:15:46.000Z","msg":"建議支那開放領空比美國軍機飛啦"},{"pid":"b5c45ec40a1c904b8c9189f794c5c3964d69fa10","tid":2100234,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad33a69a460c9051f81e595dd250cc7dee7d3d27","tid":2100234,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"下次就得返10每里<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e44ee6622f3a01a8f17ba12b7b5eb9eb244067","tid":2100234,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"支持中共派飛機去美國挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23cf5f481e6aa273a6a52df4a14390a242b05b8","tid":2100234,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"係咪做勢選總統?"},{"pid":"678589a6f8b439326aeb13a560a6d2a07ffa634d","tid":2100234,"uid":153494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"爆支國"}]}